---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AnnouncementBar from '../components/AnnouncementBar.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Equal Employment Opportunity Policy | Hamilton Exteriors"
  description="Hamilton Exteriors is an equal opportunity employer. Read our EEO policy to learn about our commitment to a diverse and inclusive workplace."
  noindex
>
  <AnnouncementBar slot="header" />
  <Navbar slot="header" />

  <section class="w-full bg-cream py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-5">
      <h1 class="font-display text-[36px] font-bold leading-tight text-[rgb(28,28,28)] md:text-[48px]">
        Equal Employment Opportunity Policy
      </h1>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-8 font-dm-sans text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: March 2026</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-[24px] font-bold text-[rgb(28,28,28)]">Our Commitment</h2>
        <p>Hamilton Exteriors, Inc. is an equal opportunity employer. We are committed to creating and maintaining a workplace where every employee, applicant, and contractor is treated with dignity and respect. We believe that a diverse team builds better homes and stronger communities, and we actively work to foster an inclusive environment where everyone can do their best work.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-[24px] font-bold text-[rgb(28,28,28)]">Protected Categories</h2>
        <p>We do not discriminate in employment on the basis of:</p>
        <ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-2">
          <li>Race or color</li>
          <li>Religion or creed</li>
          <li>Sex, including pregnancy, childbirth, and related medical conditions</li>
          <li>Gender identity or gender expression</li>
          <li>Sexual orientation</li>
          <li>National origin or ancestry</li>
          <li>Age (40 and over)</li>
          <li>Physical or mental disability</li>
          <li>Veteran or military status</li>
          <li>Genetic information</li>
          <li>Marital status</li>
          <li>Citizenship status</li>
          <li>Any other characteristic protected by applicable federal, state, or local law</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-display text-[24px] font-bold text-[rgb(28,28,28)]">Scope</h2>
        <p>This policy applies to all aspects of employment at Hamilton Exteriors, including but not limited to:</p>
        <ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-2">
          <li>Recruiting, hiring, and onboarding</li>
          <li>Compensation and benefits</li>
          <li>Training and professional development</li>
          <li>Promotions and transfers</li>
          <li>Discipline and termination</li>
          <li>Working conditions and workplace assignments</li>
          <li>Subcontractor and vendor relationships</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-display text-[24px] font-bold text-[rgb(28,28,28)]">Reasonable Accommodation</h2>
        <p>Hamilton Exteriors is committed to providing reasonable accommodations to qualified individuals with disabilities and to employees with sincerely held religious beliefs, to the extent required by law. If you need an accommodation during the application process or in your role, please contact us at (650) 977-3351 or support@hamilton-exteriors.com. We will work with you to identify a reasonable solution.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-[24px] font-bold text-[rgb(28,28,28)]">Reporting Discrimination or Harassment</h2>
        <p>If you believe you have experienced or witnessed discrimination, harassment, or retaliation in connection with Hamilton Exteriors, we encourage you to report it promptly. You can report concerns through any of the following channels:</p>
        <ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+16509773351" class="text-primary underline">(650) 977-3351</a></li>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@hamilton-exteriors.com" class="text-primary underline">support@hamilton-exteriors.com</a></li>
          <li><strong>Mail:</strong> Hamilton Exteriors, Inc., 21634 Redwood Rd Unit F, Castro Valley, CA 94546</li>
        </ul>
        <p>All reports will be taken seriously and investigated promptly. Information will be kept as confidential as possible, consistent with the need to conduct a thorough investigation.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-[24px] font-bold text-[rgb(28,28,28)]">No Retaliation</h2>
        <p>Hamilton Exteriors strictly prohibits retaliation against anyone who reports discrimination or harassment, participates in an investigation, or opposes discriminatory practices in good faith. Retaliation is itself a violation of this policy and will result in appropriate disciplinary action, up to and including termination.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-[24px] font-bold text-[rgb(28,28,28)]">Responsibility</h2>
        <p>Every employee, manager, and contractor at Hamilton Exteriors shares the responsibility of maintaining an inclusive and respectful workplace. Managers and supervisors have a particular duty to lead by example, address concerns promptly, and ensure this policy is upheld in their teams.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-[24px] font-bold text-[rgb(28,28,28)]">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this policy or need to make a report, please contact us:</p>
        <ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+16509773351" class="text-primary underline">(650) 977-3351</a></li>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@hamilton-exteriors.com" class="text-primary underline">support@hamilton-exteriors.com</a></li>
          <li><strong>Mail:</strong> Hamilton Exteriors, Inc., 21634 Redwood Rd Unit F, Castro Valley, CA 94546</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="w-full bg-white py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[600px] px-5 text-center">
      <p class="font-dm-sans text-base text-gray-600">
        Have questions about our services?
      </p>
      <a
        href="/"
        class="mt-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-primary px-8 py-3 font-dm-sans text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-primary/90"
      >
        Back to Home
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>
